  <div id="text-content_3193A260-1EFD-0135-E9B5-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="copy_course_content" data-step-uuid="cf12c37b-12ee-45aa-abb1-6849fb33266e">
    <h2 id="copy_course_content" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Copy Course Content</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/695/original/6eb66687-319c-458c-817f-3157fe18f1da.png" srcset="" alt="Copy Course Content" height="439" width="269">
