  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_current_jobs" data-step-uuid="ce669378-1e05-4129-8aff-add9f96f75fb">
    <h2 id="view_current_jobs" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Current Jobs</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/690/original/a22d3ed2-bfa3-4477-a7ad-1db54dbe173a.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/690/medium/a22d3ed2-bfa3-4477-a7ad-1db54dbe173a.png" srcset="" alt="View Current Jobs" height="177" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3195B5B0-1EFD-0135-9D06-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Current Jobs section displays the status of your import. Running reports display a progress bar indicating the time remaining to complete the import [1]. </p>
<p>If you chose to select specific content in your course, the current job will show as Waiting for Select [2], which means you must <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-select-specific-content-as-part-of-a-course-import/ta-p/1091" target="_blank">select the content you want to import</a>.</p>
<p>The import may also display other status indicators as part of the import process. Learn more about <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-view-the-status-of-current-and-prior-course-imports/ta-p/1077" target="_blank">course import statuses</a>.</p>
<p>View the content from any completed imports by accessing any link in Course Navigation.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
